lass=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6396640\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6396640\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 31, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104adi1709199038344.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/adi1709199038344.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/adi1709199038344.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"adi1709199038344\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxbutton</code> widget is a UI button control. It allows an end user to\n\t\tinvoke any kind of explicitly defined action on clicking or pressing of the\n\t\tbutton.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_pyy_dlm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e52\">Default Logical Widgets</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The default logical widget is <code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-Button</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_knr_dlm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e64\">Triggers</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">(web)trigger detail:</code> This trigger is fired when a button is pressed or\n\t\t\t\tclicked. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_qsx_clm_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e75\">Extends fluent-button Web Component</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This widget is implemented using the Fluent web component fluent-button. Most of its features\n\t\t\t\tare also available in this widget. Most of its events are mapped to triggers. For\n\t\t\t\tmore information, see the Fluent documentation on the fluent-button web\n\t\t\t\tcomponent.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_ic2_dg2_q1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e84\">Keyboard support</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When you press the <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Spacebar</kbd> key, it invokes the button that\n\t\t\t\thas focus.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_inh_lqh_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e96\">Layout processing</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Widget class method <code class=\"ph codeph\">processLayout()</code> constructs the template HTML for this\n\t\t\t\twidget. It generates nodes for the control itself as well as slots for button text\n\t\t\t\tand icon, and returns it to Uniface. Use this function to enhance the widget with\n\t\t\t\tmore static features.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_hf4_frh_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e109\">Widget properties</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxbutton</code> widget supports the following properties:<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Property</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:title</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a hover over text or tooltip, currently used as\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thelper text.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:disabled</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the widget as being disabled.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:tabindex</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Allows or prevents the widget from getting sequential focus\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tusually with the Tab key.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:hidden</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines a boolean value that hides or shows the button widget.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">html:appearance</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the appearance of the widget. The available options\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tare: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"adi1709199038344__ul_tjb_gln_tcc\">\n<li class=\"li\">neutral (default)</li>\n<li class=\"li\">accent</li>\n<li class=\"li\">outline</li>\n<li class=\"li\">lightweight</li>\n<li class=\"li\">stealth</li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">class:classname</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Boolean value that adds or removes a specified class.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">icon</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the name of the icon as it exists in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">ui-fabric-core</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlibrary.<p class=\"p\">If name is not specified, no icon is displayed.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe default is no icon.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">icon-position</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines the position of the icon. <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"adi1709199038344__note_r4y_gln_tcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"adi1709199038344__ul_s4y_gln_tcc\">\n<li class=\"li\">If position is not defined or invalid, then icon\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tposition is start of the text.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Start: The position of icon is before the text. In\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tan RTL application, the button content is shown from\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tright to left. This is a default position.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">End: The position of icon is after the text. In an\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tRTL application, the button content is shown from\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tright to left.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">exclude</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"adi1709199038344__table_yrg_krh_m1c__entry__2\">Defines that there will be no column for the field in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">uxdatagrid</code>.<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"adi1709199038344__note_uhf_fnn_tcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tis actually not a widget property. It is a field property,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tused by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxdatagrid</code> widget if that is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe containing entity's widget.</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_yvb_hdn_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e285\">Helper and validation error visualization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">A <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxbutton</code> does not allow changing the field value interactively,\n\t\t\t\tthus the field values might still be incorrect for various reasons. This means that\n\t\t\t\tthe button needs to report the behavior. Hence, an exception is thrown from the\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">showError()</code> function.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_vnb_ndn_m1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e300\">UI blocking</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When the field is in transaction, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uxbutton</code> widget blocks user\n\t\t\t\tinput by becoming inactive. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"adi1709199038344__section_c4l_z4m_41c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d354089e312\">Widget styling</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"adi1709199038344__table_wgx_4sk_q1c_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"adi1709199038344__table_wgx_4sk_q1c_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"adi1709199038344__table_wgx_4sk_q1c\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" id=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" name=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-CSS Selector-0-0\">CSS Selector</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" id=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" name=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Selected node(s)-1-0\">Selected node(s)</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label